data.description: Ready to buy a home but worried about interest rates? No Worries Here! 2.5% assumable mortgage for this 4 bdrm, 2 bath, classic Florida block home. Nothing says classic Florida like Terrazzo floors and funky, cool retro bathroom tiles!  Huge fenced back yard with 2 sheds (1 w/power), and fire pit to enjoy our cool Florida winters.  Cost efficient hurricane impact windows (2023), slider door (2023), gas dryer, new gas hot water heater, and new A/C. Primary suite has an adjoined office/nursery/sitting area, open living/dining room combo, and split bedroom plan.  This location is fabulous... close to schools, shopping, AND views of the VAB.  Watch launches from your front yard! This home is oozing with possibilities!!
